window.bookSummaryJSON = "Little Irene Miller studies her face in the mirror as she prepares for her performance under the big top, though Siamese twins and clowns are a far cry from dancing with Buster Keaton. The circus may be changing their lineup, and the last girl who left ended up in an alley with her skirt hiked up. \"Best Wishes, Irene Miller\" is a short horror story that appears in M.J. Pack's collection <i>Certain Dark Things</i>, also available on Audible.com."; 
